Wordpress Admin Page Class
=======================
Contributors: bainternet
Requires at least: 3.1
Tested up to: 3.3.1

Description
-----------
Admin Page Class

The Admin Page Class is used by including it in your plugin files and using its methods to 
create custom Admin Pages. It is meant to be very simple and straightforward. 

Usage
--------
Take a look at the `class-usage-demo.php` file which can also be tested as a WordPress Plugin. 
Other options are available for each field which can be see in the 'admin-page-class.php' file, 


